snippet.title: Skull Scavenger | Official Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Skull Scavenger is an unforgiving twin-stick Extraction Looter Shooter where you are a soul trying to get out of hell. Drift across 4 realms defeating the greater demons, slam into enemies, reflect bullets, collect new weapons and treasure. Escape before your skull is shattered or lose everything! 

WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2557470/Skull_Scavenger/

Play the demo on itch.io
https://evil-villain-games.itch.io/skull-scavanger

Music from Free Music Archive
Artist Keosz
Song Glib
